Manchester United Doesn’t Put Berbatov in the Squad Against Barcelona

-- B y   C h r i s   E l s e r
-- 
2011-05-28T18:09:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-28/manchester-united-doesn-t-put-berbatov-in-the-squad-against-barcelona.html
Manchester United  coach Alex Ferguson
decided not to put Dimitar Berbatov in the squad for tonight’s
Champions League final against Barcelona.  Michael Owen will be on the bench in place of the striker,
according to a team sheet released at Wembley Stadium in  London ,
where the match will be held. Barcelona will start defender
Carles Puyol on the bench.  United lineup: van der Sar, Evra, Ferdinand, Rooney, Giggs,
Park, Hernandez, Vidic, Carrick, Fabio, Valencia. Subs:
Kuszczak, Owen, Anderson, Smalling, Nani, Scholes, Fletcher.  Barcelona lineup: Valdes, Alves, Pique, Hernandez, Villa,
Iniesta, Messi, Mascherano, Busquets, Pedro Rodriguez, Abidal.
Subs: Olazabal, Puyol, Krkic, Keita, Afellay, Adriano,
Alcantara.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  